                                                        .col-md-12
                                                            br
                                                            .x_content
                                                                .row
                                                                    .col-md-12.col-sm-4.col-xs-12.profile_details
                                                                        .well.profile_view(style='width:100%')
                                                                            .col-xs-12
                                                                                center
                                                                                    h2     
                                                                                        br
                                                                                        | Type of Request:
